help:
AiAeBot by Daniel

 User commands:
.ships | List with all ships
.getavatar name | Returns user avatar
.mf name | Returns Middle Finger selfie
.8ball text | Give answer to your question
.kys text | Question

 Moderator commands:
.addship name name | Ship people
.rship name name | Remove ship
.mute name reason | Mute someone with fun reason
.unmute name | Remove mute
.addrole name role | User, Pleb and Cute Grill
.purge name int | Delete user messages

 Owner commands:
.setnick name | Change bot nick
.status text | Change playing status
.setavatar url | Change bot avatar
.shutdown | Dead
